{"tid":1525520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方昨日在西環拘捕8人 涉藏有攻擊性武器","createTime":"2019-09-01T01:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T01:45:01.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c607c2bb5e24bf301463a86131fe119efafeda7","tid":1525520,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:11:18.000Z","msg":"警方表示，昨日中午在銅鑼灣一間酒店房間，檢獲一批保護裝備包括頭盔、裝甲等，以及「鐳射槍」與超過40000元現金，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器，拘捕房間內3名介乎16至26歲的男子，案件由毒品調查科跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方又說，昨日西環有人報案說，有人在街上藏有攻擊性武器。警方到場發現有介乎19至35歲的6男2女，正處理武器及物品，警員上前截查，檢獲通渠水、噴漆、斧頭、棒球、電動棒球發射器、懷疑假記者證等，8人涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被捕。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478105-20190901.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478105-20190901.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=6c81b5ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478105-20190901.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=28497a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478105-20190901.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"91ad44df348eb217122b2b369e1648fd34e44fad","tid":1525520,"uid":242083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"831恐襲同721恐襲冇分別<br />\n我正式宣佈香港警察係有牌黑社會兼恐怖分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeYzNsiOy00o&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=abc532e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o</a>"},{"pid":"83fb4294d3e84581dedca5d3c60b87452fd4b655","tid":1525520,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c607c2bb5e24bf301463a86131fe119efafeda7","tid":1525520,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:11:18.000Z","msg":"警方表示，昨日中午在銅鑼灣一間酒店房間，檢獲一批保護裝備包括頭盔、裝甲等，以及「鐳射槍」與超過40000元現金，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器，拘捕房間內3名介